	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, most of us have the same problems (not having all the skills to single handedly make a great game)<br /><br />Probably you should visit a music forum (such as famitracker forum) and search for a chiptune musician.<br /><br />And, then search for a pixel artist somewhere. Maybe Twitter or Reddit or something.<br /><br />And, you should probably have a cool game idea, that you can get people interested in being a part of.<br /><br />Then you just need to do the &quot;easy&quot; part, programming and designing a game.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


